The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | Damika in doubt for 2nd Test
                                                                                                                       7                                      Damika in doubt for 2nd Test
            OUR CORRESPONDENT                      
	Ahmedabad: Damika Prasad is in doubt for the second Test after suffering a hamstring injury.         
	He didnt bowl in the first session but sent down four overs in the final session on Friday. Dilhara Fernando, who was called in as Thilan Thusaras replacement, has joined the side.         
	Meanwhile, Tillekaratne Dilshan got injured during a round of football on Friday evening. Later, a team member said he was fine.                                                                                                                     
